overview:
BuyStrategy.com is an online provider of consulting-quality business strategy frameworks. It is founded by a team of management consultants who have acquired expertise in the areas of corporate strategy, operations/supply chain, financial analysis, presentation development, and financial modeling.

BuyStrategy’s business strategy frameworks have been used by Fortune 500 companies, strategy consulting firms, and top MBA programs. The site also offers other business presentation materials, such as PowerPoint templates and diagrams.
